<question>
  Unus duo tres.

  <answer>
    One two three.
  </answer>
</question>

<question>
  Unus ursus.

  <answer>
    A bear.

    Ursa Major 是西方的大熊星座，中国称北斗七星。

    "Unity" and "unite" are from "unus".
  </answer>
</question>

<question>
  Duo ursi.

  <answer>
    Two bears.
  </answer>
</question>

<question>
  Tres vaccae.

  <answer>
    Three cows.
  </answer>
</question>

<question>
  One cow.

  <answer>
    Una vacca.

    The first three numbers decline with the noun.

    "Vaccine" comes from "vacca".

    疫苗首次发现于得了天花的牛。
  </answer>
</question>

<question>
  Two cows.

  <answer>
    Duae vaccae.

    The first three numbers decline with the noun.
  </answer>
</question>

<question>
  One cat.

  <answer>
    Una felis.

    "Felis" is a feminine noun.
  </answer>
</question>

<question>
  Two cats.

  <answer>
    Unae feles.
  </answer>
</question>

<cloze>
  Declensions of the first three numbers.

  Nominative case only.

  | number | masculine | feminine |

